Package: GroupHW
Type: Package
Title: K-Means and Multiclass Logistic Regression with Rcpp
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-11-11
Author: Fu, Ziang and Zhu, Zhiyuan
Maintainer: Fu, Ziang <ziangfu@tamu.edu>
Description: Provides R and C++ (via 'Rcpp' and 'RcppArmadillo') implementations of 
    K-means clustering and multiclass logistic regression fitted by a damped Newton 
    method with ridge regularization. Includes R wrappers with input validation and 
    C++ cores for performance.
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.5)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Encoding: UTF-8
